## What Was Built

### 1. 🏨 Room Assignment with Conflict Detection
**File:** [app/components/Bookings.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Laksh/hotel-admin/app/components/Bookings.tsx)

- **Visual Room Picker** replaces the old dropdown — rooms shown as a grid of buttons
- Rooms are color-coded: 🟦 Selected · 🔴 Occupied (date conflict) · ⬜ Available
- Conflict detection is automatic: selecting overlapping dates marks affected rooms red
- Double-booking is **not possible** — the Save button is disabled if a conflict exists

### 2. 👥 Multi-Occupant / Co-Guest Management
**File:** [app/components/Bookings.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Laksh/hotel-admin/app/components/Bookings.tsx)

- Booking modal now has **3 tabs**: Booking / Guests / Special
- **Guests tab**: Primary guest at top, dynamic Add Guest list below
- Each co-guest captures: Name, Passport/ID, Nationality, DOB, Phone, Dietary Pref
- Co-guest count shown on booking cards and list view ("+2 co")

### 3. ⚙️ Early Check-in / Late Check-out
**File:** [app/components/Bookings.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Laksh/hotel-admin/app/components/Bookings.tsx)

- **Special tab** in booking modal has checkboxes for Early CI / Late CO
- Time pickers appear when either is enabled
- Flags shown on calendar chips, list view, and in Reports

### 4. 👔 Staff Management (New Page)
**File:** [app/components/Staff.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Laksh/hotel-admin/app/components/Staff.tsx) + [app/api/staff/route.ts](file:///c:/Users/Laksh/hotel-admin/app/api/staff/route.ts)

- **On Shift Now** roster card based on current time
- **Department Overview** — click to filter by role
- Full staff directory with role/shift filters and search
- Inline **attendance marking** per staff (Present/Absent/Late)
- Add/Edit/Delete modal with all fields

### 5. 🍽️ Meal Plan CRUD
**File:** [app/components/MealPlans.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Laksh/hotel-admin/app/components/MealPlans.tsx) + [app/api/meal-plans/route.ts](file:///c:/Users/Laksh/hotel-admin/app/api/meal-plans/route.ts)

- Plan cards now have Edit + Delete buttons
- **Add Plan modal**: code, name, description, price, active toggle, included meals picker
- Included meals shown as colored pills per plan
- Adoption statistics (# bookings, # guests) shown per plan

### 6. 🔧 Maintenance Full Redesign
**File:** [app/components/Maintenance.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Laksh/hotel-admin/app/components/Maintenance.tsx)

- **Card layout** with left colored priority border
- Horizontal status + priority badges (no more cramped stacking)
- **Quick-action buttons**: → Working · ✓ Resolve (no modal required)
- **Comment timeline** per issue with expandable panel
- **Kanban view** toggle (4 columns: Open → In Progress → Resolved → Deferred)
- SLA timer shows hours/days since reported
- Added: Category, Estimated Cost, comment system

### 7. 📊 Reports & Night Audit (New Page)
**File:** [app/components/Reports.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Laksh/hotel-admin/app/components/Reports.tsx)

5 tabs:
- **Occupancy** — per room type, bar chart, date range picker
- **Arrivals & Departures** — 7-day forward view with flags
- **In-House List** — live table of checked-in guests with nights remaining
- **Revenue** — by source · by meal plan · by room type, bar breakdowns
- **Night Audit** — daily summary, no-show detector, housekeeping snapshot, close audit button

### 8. 🌱 Updated Seed Data
**File:** [app/api/seed/route.ts](file:///c:/Users/Laksh/hotel-admin/app/api/seed/route.ts)

- **12 realistic staff members** across all departments
- Seed now loads: customers, bookings, meal plans, housekeeping, maintenance, pricing rules, **staff**
- "Load Demo Data" button in topbar refreshes all collections

