## How to Use

1. **Load demo data:** Click **"🌱 Load Demo Data"** in the topbar
2. **Book a room with conflict detection:** Bookings → New Booking → select a room type → pick dates → see the room grid with live conflict highlighting
3. **Add co-guests:** Bookings → New/Edit Booking → Guests tab → Add Guest
4. **Staff roster:** Staff (sidebar) → see who's currently on shift at the top
5. **Night audit:** Reports & Audit → Night Audit tab → review day-end summary → Close Audit
6. **Maintenance kanban:** Maintenance → click ⬛ Kanban button → drag-free board view
